OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLikely
OL,6,Fwet and windy at first Friday, then
OL,7,Fcooler with showers. Saturday starts
OL,8,Foff settled before rain arrives during
OL,9,Fthe evening. Rain easing on Sunday and
OL,10,Fturning mild again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
